CellWidth: The width of each sprite in grid mode
CellHeight: The height of each sprite in grid mode
NumCellsX: Number of cells extracted horizontally. Can be used to limit the number of sprites extracted. Set to 0 to extract all sprites
NumCellsY: Number of cells extracted vertically. Can be used to limit the number of sprites extracted. Set to 0 to extract all sprites
MarginX: Margin from the left of the texture to the first sprite
MarginY: Margin from the top of the texture to the first sprite
